                ["title1"] = "【灵鸟之证】活动说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_灵鸟之证.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"XwDRdiql4ooKbTxnghVc6uY3nHd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QJwVdwad2ouKa3xVgiuciFrLnsf\">梦中的灵鸟为你衔来新枝，带来更多挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EQFxd5y8KovWdlxfrsrcHlScnum\">通关限时灵鸟试炼，获取活动奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnePFMo0TlBsOR3w3OvtsvUh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn5Hq4ENqHyXOCrud6PTbPyc\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHaNdJCwgo7kOjxIVTxcGkCPnJ3\">2026年1月5日 10:00 ~ 2026年1月26日 05:00 （UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnfOhANDfkQJ1nC6ecOgjDeh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn2uAP2x33PuwolfbzLQvdch\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnzus7KC3fD3sdoSEd7WtAlv\">完成夜航篇剧情【前往少女所说的宅邸】并开启【活动】功能</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnuV20elAGneFtdag2AuPgGc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnaTiTMvtsFeJD8Gfk6cdDJS\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn1HsSBXMed9zOrh52sPe1vd\">「委托密函线索」「深红凝珠」「战斗旋律&middot;三」「武器说明书&middot;三」「皎皎之民的信物」「铜币」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn444wEKnnqqjKJZcVdaOpsb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn3fKWRMSAaCSJEfnSj6fRnc\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQvV1n4XPDQ9xcGJGyW76yc\">活动期间将开启限时灵鸟试炼关卡。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CJVodZSmqoNENUxqMosctwdtnZc\">完成灵鸟试炼的挑战目标即可获得星级奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZaQodXi8RoKTJSxLiF7cuDSvnje\">累计达到指定星级后，可领取活动奖励。</div>\n</div>",
