                ["title1"] = "【轰鸣演练】活动说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_轰鸣演练.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\">这是对精度的特训，是对炮火的校验。瞄准开炮！达成所有演练目标吧。</p>\n<div data-page-id=\"MIHNdyoUroPGzexg0NvcaZYsnIe\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnU6cJ37Ctvfqf4jNnfW1wnf\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnSTfBZVtAbBpqfm1oYTyUEf\">2026年1月20日 10:00 ~ 2026年2月10日 维护前（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcndHxoiyEnjl0VI3pzozjXVe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvXznZIFy8wl81VqgesZqNh\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnjvv1qJf97Aeg4DTb3PqFhc\">完成夜航篇剧情【前往少女所说的宅邸】并开启【活动】功能</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnHpao46o4keCUhtdX1k1tXc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcncfqAZFXkBWNvQfu3H7rJvc\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZWS6JytecijhUwMXVAk5Wf\">「委托密函线索」「皎皎之民的信物」「战斗旋律&middot;三」「武器说明书&middot;三」「深红凝珠」「铜币」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnjonbvTKVdtzVGoQP7gNO7w\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcneRci4fhrJ8KwJq8fv26yXb\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn50e4pCTs030dCO60eeNLDh\">在【<strong>轰鸣演练</strong>】活动中共有7个关卡，狩月人需要操作机关大炮，阻止关卡中的敌人进入传送门。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-A3IndMrT8onTzXx8gXFcEOFgnGd\">在关卡中击败敌方单位即可获得演练积分，每个活动关卡都有累计的目标积分，达到指定目标积分后即可领取演练奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ua2SdPrVzoqizkxSGk2cTtLinwh\">随着活动关卡推进还可解锁机关大炮的配件，从而大幅度增强机关大炮的火力，合理搭配配件，可以更加轻松的完成演练。</div>\n</div>",
