            [1] = {
                ["title1"] = "侍者皎皎的商店上新",
                ["body"] = "<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-LK1Xde2rFoppSpxd2V3cAtv7n4d\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>★【烟津闻弦】上架★</strong></span></h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/吟游诗集&middot;烟津闻弦.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"DfMgdz42ioiWQVxCpX3ctopVnvf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OaHUdc2GwoDtESxAcLbcbrIHnFh\">※ 解锁【典藏诗集】即可获得「闻香自选形象礼箱&middot;墨玉」*1!</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FT1fdTp9zoRVDPxUWsrcH0fMnah\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYfjdmE5boY0dyxplXScBBEznqb\"><strong>【开启时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LCB3dheilootVqxHElDcU3yQnOc\"><strong>烟津闻弦I：</strong>2025年12月23日开服后 ~ 2026年1月20日 05:00 （UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MTDJd6J8moSy75xruD3cSAlvnNg\"><strong>烟津闻弦Ⅱ：</strong>2026年1月20日 05:00 ~ 2026年2月10日维护前 （UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QmEnd4j9MoDEhvxPtBJcGQO0nVf\">【烟津闻弦Ⅱ】开启时间共计持续3周，为了各位狩月人的体验，【烟津闻弦Ⅱ】的【转述见闻】中会额外增加不受每周上限限制的【见闻任务】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JLPYdHllSohYZcxtPVRca3aJn7e\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Hsnyd0Ih1oLThVx9TuIcGnNZn4e\"><strong>【吟游诗集说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ULOXdRZq0oNssaxwO19cBS7pnxs\">&bull; 活动期间，狩月人可通过完成吟游诗集的见闻任务提升诗歌段落等级，领取丰厚奖励。每期吟游诗集开启后，将默认解锁平装诗集。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zh2lduU2RopTA1xLi45cw8zzncg\">&bull; 解锁【精装诗集】并提升诗歌段落等级可获得「自选魔灵」、「月石」、「华彩沙漏」、「移转模块」、「武器移转模块」、「暮夜的履迹」、「委托手册」、「深红凝珠」等奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EFPIdbz6BobxwMxvWg9cXurGnig\">&bull; 解锁【典藏诗集】，除以上奖励外，可立即提升10级诗歌段落等级，还可额外获得「月石」*200、「委托手册&middot;三」*5以及「闻香自选形象礼箱&middot;墨玉」*1奖励！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EFPIdbz6BobxwMxvWg9cXurGnig\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EFPIdbz6BobxwMxvWg9cXurGnig\">\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\"><strong><span class=\"text-only\" data-eleid=\"3\">【当前限定奖励说明】</span></strong></div>\n<div data-lark-html-role=\"root\"><span class=\"text-only\" data-eleid=\"5\">吟游诗集将产出以下限定奖励</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EFPIdbz6BobxwMxvWg9cXurGnig\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DfMgdz42ioiWQVxCpX3ctopVnvf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-In2jdzgEuoOvucxUyTZchS31nBc\">烟津闻弦I：「头像&middot;我的你好箱」「展示动作&middot;林梢日光」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Shj7dtPKRorHwdxz0MtcNgWjnwc\">烟津闻弦Ⅱ：「头像&middot;画太阳」「展示动作&middot;高雅人士」</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NjkddAUugoxAojxyH5Rc2KAznzh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZOLud8ATVoloaIxjD6wcFU7Snhe\"><strong>【</strong><strong>闻香</strong><strong>自选形象奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QYwqdTJ4FoPtKOxmPqgcAzLjnAD\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LjmQdWzCeoIrI5x1S2kcDWEfnzf\">开启时可从扶疏、刻舟、贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Kv7JdFbrsodbdcxwftFcwEt0nYc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UIRDdVngco87YOxILsBccDjOnAg\"><strong>【自选魔灵奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-A3SwddKWToGnEyxC44OchyG1nEd\">吟游诗集达到30级并解锁【精装诗集】或【典藏诗集】，可从以下五星魔灵中自选召唤一只：「堇青艾尔芙」、「碧玺艾尔芙」、「玛瑙艾尔芙」、「紫晶艾尔芙」、「黑曜艾尔芙」、「欧泊艾尔芙」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DOxqdVHO7oudApxyuZLcAhKNnGd\">召唤魔灵后，可在【整备】-【魔灵】界面进行查看和装配。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DOxqdVHO7oudApxyuZLcAhKNnGd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DOxqdVHO7oudApxyuZLcAhKNnGd\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-C5rUdUKvVoxehlxyj19cQm9RnWf\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>★</strong>【外观组合礼箱&middot;星芒】上架<strong>★</strong></span></h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DOxqdVHO7oudApxyuZLcAhKNnGd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DfMgdz42ioiWQVxCpX3ctopVnvf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZFprdbHeyoRqYSxCrhlcIgOenob\">【礼包上架时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YyVgdqTU7o0rgDxzMY7c620Snye\">2025年12月23日更新后 ~ 2026年2月10日维护前</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YzYAdv2xboQ3JMxvIX7cFb5Tnbb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-URCgdTyVhoN6hmxGf77cYopKnPx\">【礼包说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\">购买后可获得「启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒」以及「星霜光轮」「星霜胡须」「星霜羽翼」「星霜雪人」配饰。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DfMgdz42ioiWQVxCpX3ctopVnvf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-SKp4dHThdoi4bax6MkbcKRSgnJ8\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>★【闻香自选形象礼箱&middot;墨玉】上架★</strong></span></h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_闻香自选形象礼盒.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MHmNdSnWpoctYexv5fscDtnEnWd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DfMgdz42ioiWQVxCpX3ctopVnvf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ITO4dcplvojqRFxr9DScxpo1nId\"><strong>【礼包上架时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P778dYDnUok9VoxHzfocy50YnTh\">2025年12月23日开服后</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KqxTdCHPmo5zlExO6YScxgetnsC\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FcLqdNI8donDa1x3QsxcB2l3nvb\"><strong>【礼包售价】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PCdQdG7dBoHyjvxE4rJcde4Un0e\">「月石晶胚」*1280</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ev3pd6oHFoo3FcxmeBNcHYoCnWg\"><strong>【活动限时折扣】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-POfmdyQXVokgo0x5hExcrBv0n5c\">活动期间首次购买，优惠价「月石晶胚」*780；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZoAid3SedobpWlxBfaicTwBGnxd\">二次购买，优惠价「月石晶胚」*980，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ek94dzp0fo3lpixm07Hcodtcn2b\">活动结束后或购买2次后将恢复原价。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GbbHdEfWgoVH2rxnOVvc9n2BnU2\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GXTEdqv3yoaltjx9o0ecXJksnVb\"><strong>【折扣时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TZApdFrfiox1UzxfHdIcWZ29nQg\">2025年12月23日开服后 ~ 2026年2月10日 维护前</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WZHpdi1u2oPsLsxSBkxcvIlxnHh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NXrtdFxMsot8uKxSgWTcAaFdnwe\"><strong>【闻香自选形象奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D9nDdjycJoABcqxfRAmcYrpin8c\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ICQtdtIfDoeoPdxApDocJHLQnPd\">开启时可从扶疏、刻舟、贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HPs7dBpUJoKPT7xDbAUc9QMJnTc\">*如提前选择刻舟形象，可在后续获得角色刻舟时直接使用。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HPs7dBpUJoKPT7xDbAUc9QMJnTc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HPs7dBpUJoKPT7xDbAUc9QMJnTc\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_狩月人形象礼盒.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HPs7dBpUJoKPT7xDbAUc9QMJnTc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-li