                ["title1"] = "【委托密函】止流委托密函轮换说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/密函轮换预告_728x200-止流-简中.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"CLjSdtvo0oOI3zx2u7DccF7CnHd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnUzZ7Fy3FnEJ6gqK4RFpzid\">委托密函将于2026年2月10日 更新后进行轮换，以下为轮换规则。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZ059uirooyaFuL3OVQ3fCc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn20j6HKCgGrKwPKRI1Keywg\">2026年2月10日 更新后：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnXjs2j7b3H2GPQDVmytgnhh\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 100, 218);\"><strong>「密函：止流」「密函：万古的诀别」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：刻舟」「密函：若华的飞光」</strong></span>进入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnM5ISNYlyHM7ung72kFrong\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：刻舟」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：海尔法」</strong></span>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnJQUm68Vizd6qjITqcPOB6d\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：若华的飞光」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：惩戒的炼火」</strong></span>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnU23pv41xDLZIbeqwrqhgfe\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：风云决」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：鎏金岁月」</strong></span>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnG7QUqNQh3oOC8X6Rovhwof\"><strong>&bull;</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：海尔法」</strong><strong>「密函：惩戒的炼火」「密函：鎏金岁月」</strong></span>将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnkOX3f0r8XbbpYIG50RkX3e\">特别提醒：本次梦魇残声奖励轮换时间为2月10日（周二），更新后<strong>不会重置</strong>梦魇残声周奖励次数，若想获取<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：刻舟」「密函：若华的飞光」「密函：风云决」</strong></span>的狩月人，请根据自身需求安排游玩挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnseK35NFTuaBMfJhhpOAhoe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnUUYNHRQejsSp3az6S10vvb\">随着本次沉浸式戏剧更新，剧目中的【舞台伴奏】与【推荐属性】也会一同进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnb8sse9GWel4SGpe4HtZ5vc\">本期推荐属性：<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">光属性</span>、<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 100, 218);\">雷属性</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnuyt6LP8ovTSvSAwFXL5Hdb\">本期【舞台伴奏】将会轮换一批新的&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;，以下为【不朽剧目】中部分&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnuyt6LP8ovTSvSAwFXL5Hdb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnuyt6LP8ovTSvSAwFXL5Hdb\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 121, 121);\">▍更多【舞台伴奏】可在版本更新后进入游戏内查看。</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FRHCdV5dhoQm9hx8LL4c5vIHnec\">●【抉择变奏：元素契约】：敌方单位获得选定的元素属性，受到的克制属性伤害提高400%，非克制属性伤害降低50%</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FoTEdumYcoiZkVxOG4Lc4INJnBb\">●【活跃急板：辉煌岁月】：友方单位释放战技或终结技时，获得昂扬提高60%，持续18秒。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HifTdckQvovKM0xlJQacQG4knpb\">●【活跃急板：众志成城】：友方单位施放战技或终结技时，获得造成的技能伤害提高10.0%效果，持续15秒，最多叠加9层，满层时，受到伤害时不会产生僵直。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U1yAdmWZwo4BXVx9xe9c0Xd9nAe\">●【防御变奏：胆小重骑士】：敌方单位受到伤害降低80%，每次受到伤害时，伤害降低幅度降低1.0%。</div>\n</div>",
